thread.title: Chris

author: Chris
title: Chris
text:
I meet with 3 agents before deciding Matthew was the best choice. He filled me with a sense of confidence that he and his team would deliver the best possible result and the process would be easy.
And it was. Matthew arranged for photos, recommended and introduced a fantastic stylist, organised several maintenance issues to be fixed and kept me up to speed every step of the way.
Above all, the sale price exceeded my expectation.
For that reason alone, I would highly recommend Nelson Alexander to anyone selling.
Thanks Matthew and Nelson Alexander.
